{"tid":1841582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"個政府廢撚到咁，係應該被架空","createTime":"2020-01-25T10:08:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T11:15:37.000Z","uid":198684,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e544cec7292f45b13d24c4a179ae58f161898285","tid":1841582,"uid":198684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:08:12.000Z","msg":"離地到唔可以用筆墨去形容<br />\n<br />\n佢哋嘅思維已經唔係瀨咁撚簡單<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依個政府所有防疫前線支援冇做過❌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有嘢都係靠緊守崗位既醫療團隊<br />\n<br />\n同埋各民間組織確保口罩供應<br />\n<br />\n以及自發教導大眾防疫工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府已經形同虛設<br />\n<br />\n市民聲音聽唔到都算<br />\n<br />\n但林閪已經去到一個比獨裁咁可惡既地步<br />\n<br />\n就係只為同反對聲音對著幹<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mkM0OGL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmkM0OGL.jpg&h=aa753614&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出黎除咗廢話之外對疫情完全冇任何幫助<br />\n<br />\n如果各位仲係望政府打掛的話真係死路一條"},{"pid":"d1831bc4fc19fe0347aaf69ef41acc31e85d02eb","tid":1841582,"uid":265179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:09:46.000Z","msg":"都係個句, 佢有30000警狗, 武力係佢個邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8061d3acb895c30ed857a652b5716dbc8d716cb","tid":1841582,"uid":99397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:10:47.000Z","msg":"真，本身都唔諗住睇，知實廢話。<br />\n睇左一分鐘已經火滾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a06042e44e8966d11ba3f0066374f653ca0f9bbf","tid":1841582,"uid":198684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1831bc4fc19fe0347aaf69ef41acc31e85d02eb","tid":1841582,"uid":265179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:09:46.000Z","msg":"都係個句, 佢有30000警狗, 武力係佢個邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:1